
Korean romanized input method with hanja words, brute version with a HUGE dictionary.

This input method for RIME is made for my friend, who is a language teacher, speaks a lot of languages.

You can contact me using Chinese/Japanese/English.
Sorry that I cannot understand Korean without kr-ja Google Translation.

-------------------------

韩文（包括汉字词）罗马音输入法，为每个词列举三类可能的罗马音组合。大词典暴力制作。

此作品初衷为简化一友人之工作，而笔者目前不懂韩文，或多有欠佳处理，但愿不会阻碍您的日常使用。

-------------------------
Reference:

30k-hanja list : Choe Hwanjin / https://github.com/choehwanjin/libhangul
36k-words list : https://github.com/acidsound/korean_wordlist
romanize rules : https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Revised_Romanization_of_Korean
util code used : https://github.com/choehwanjin/libhangul

Based on RIME  : https://github.com/rime

Thanks for all these works!

